            <lg xml:id="TK1284">
<l>ūṭalkaṭ ceṉṟēṉmaṉ ṟōḻi yatumaṟantu </l>
<l>kūṭaṟkaṭ ceṉṟateṉ ṉeñcu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O my friend! I was prepared to feign displeasure but my mind forgetting it was ready to embrace him.</l>
